git vs github
git is the version control software that runs locally on machine, it doesnt need internet, you can use git without ever touching github

github:
it is a service that takes git repositories or projects, hosts them in the cloud and makes
it easier to collaborate with other people.
we need to sign kup for an accouint to use github.its onlline place to share work that
